{"tid":1912613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(棄城而逃?) 10箱緊急物資武漢運北京","createTime":"2020-03-06T07:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T08:09:31.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"54d4de7052874dcb28d4642c7391eeb05c78c20a","tid":1912613,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:52:21.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】在交通運輸部緊急運輸任務指令保障下，4日16時37分許，中國紅十字會10箱緊急物資從湖北省武漢市通過鐵路方式運送。《北京日報》客戶端稱， 這批緊急物資預計昨夜抵達北京西站。官方未透露10箱緊急物資的詳細情况，知情人士指， 該批物資包括研製的新冠疫苗及檢測試劑，另外可能包括康復者的血漿。作為新冠肺炎疫情重災區，緊急物資從武漢運出較為罕見。4日晚，800箱共計2萬套防護服，由北京西站運往武漢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/article/20200306/s00013/1583433537352/10%E7%AE%B1%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E7%89%A9%E8%B3%87%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E9%81%8B%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2Farticle%2F20200306%2Fs00013%2F1583433537352%2F10%25E7%25AE%25B1%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E7%2589%25A9%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcNjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=f03d155f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2Farticle%2F20200306%2Fs00013%2F1583433537352%2F10%25E7%25AE%25B1%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E7%2589%25A9%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC&h=2cb4745e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/article/20200306/s00013/1583433537352/10%E7%AE%B1%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E7%89%A9%E8%B3%87%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E9%81%8B%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC</a>"},{"pid":"6965860db89d6a6c724685ae945533de82a0441d","tid":1912613,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:53:39.000Z","msg":"北京有政治局常委奶撚咗嘢啊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2258024235adf5e0b07b8868874acb1444cb4